Tab1Text1:
Welcome to the server!

First of all, have a great time!

This is a PVE server, so treat each other with respect. Any misbehavior will be punished. Be sure to read and accept the server rules by pressing the F3 key (go to the website, log in via Steam, and at the bottom of the page, there will be a notification that will give you the opportunity to accept the rules).

For voting for the server, you will receive 200 tokens. The links to the pages where you can vote can be found under the F3 key.

Information about other servers and your statistics can be found on our website: sgservers.eu

If you have any questions, join our Discord; we will be happy to answer them there.

Regards,
SG
Tab1Text2:
IMPORTANT INFORMATION:

The shop where you can pick up the Starter Kit can be found under the F2 key.

Structure and creature decay is active on all servers. Decay settings:
- Thatch: 12 Days
- Wood: 24 Days
- Stone: 36 Days
- Metal: 48 Days
- Creatures: 24 Days

Chat Commands:
- !kill /kill
- !suicide /suicide

These commands allow you to kill your own character (to get unstuck, etc.).

- !claim /claim

This command allows you to claim your votes.
